							About Us						




















 Patents

BioConsortia's prorietary AMS technology is a novel and efficient discovery platform for microbial products. Process patents convering our unique selection methods will allow BioConsortia to maintain a prominent position in the plant microbiome space. BioConsortia has a series of pending patent applications covering elements of AMS, as well as pending patent applications for specific identified consortia for agricultural applications.
 
Issued patents:
Accelerated Directed Evolution of Microbial Consortia for the Development of Desirable Plant Phenotypic Traits
