EXCLUSIVE: Davis ag technology company raises $8 million equity round




Nov 2, 2016, 2:48pm PDT






Industries & Tags


                    Technology,                 



                    Food & Lifestyle,                 


            Agriculture             














Mark Anderson


Staff Writer
Sacramento Business Journal













                    Share
                


























